					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<div class="vip__experience">
				<h3 class="vip__experience-heading">Passport Lounge Watch Party</h3>
				<p class="vip__experience-description">Explore three unique themed lounges across Downtown Burbank, each offering its own vibe for watching the match.</p>
